On beautiful Daniel Island, where the breeze drifts through the live oaks and the evening light lingers, Vinea invites you to slow down, savor, and connect. Relax with European-inspired dishes, delightful wines, and genuine hospitality! More About Us Hours Tuesday – Thursday | 5PM – 9PMFriday – Saturday | 5PM – 9PM Our Menu Fresh flavors. Inspired by Europe. Fresh, approachable dishes inspired by European flavors — made with passion and served with warmth.
